														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2011072">
									

<p>I'm very close to upvoting. The writing was done well enough to keep me interested, and the level of detail of how the site and 017's containment chamber worked added some nice immersion. I didn't much care for the detailed background on the characters; it broke the flow of the story, and if knowing these guys' histories was essential (I'd say it's probably more relevant to the dude changing the bulb), it may have been better to communicate that in ways other than stopping the action cold and giving us a paragraph.</p>
<p>Neutral vote for now, but overall a decent job.</p>

