			<div class="content" id="post-content-2011079">
									

<blockquote>
<p>What utter irony it would be, for one containment breach to occur because the efforts of preventing a breach interfered with another object's containment!</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Heh, I see what you did there (I think).</p>
<p>Anyway, I liked this a lot. You get so used to incident reports and interview logs sometimes you forget that there's a real story behind it.</p>
<p>E: Oh, also.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Lloyd Swinburne nodded, <strong>feel</strong> more drained than he had ever been.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This was the main error that stood out to me, other than that it was pretty good.</p>

